Extraordinary Music Supervisor Jen Malone, known for her work on the hit FX show, @atlantafx joins us for Episode 24. We talk to Jen about her start in the music business on the east coast, doing PR for rock bands, and eventually moving her way out west to become a music supervisor. Afterwards, we talk about her ascent into the world of supervision, from interning at Format Entertainment to supervising shows of her own, including Atlanta, Lady Dynamite on Netflix, and MTV's Are You The One? In news, we discuss the new YouTube series "Best.Cover.Ever" and 2016 financial results from Sony Music Entertainment. @jenmalone666
